::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Reptilica looks up from his work, frowning. "Zardus asked you to help? 
Allright. I'm Reptilica, this one's Bloodystrike," he motions to Bloodystrike 
as if the other was a foreign object, "Who are you two?"

Bloodystrike growls at Reptilica, turning to look at the two other bots.
